results.description:
Loose-fitting, lined, below hip jacket has notched collar, shoulder pads, yokes and long, two-piece sleeves cut-in-one, flaps, welt pockets and belt.  Straight, lined skirt, above mid-knee, has waistband and back zipper and hemline slit.  Purchased belt.  Bodysuit has contrast collar, fitted, front pleated bodice, panties with snap front closing, elastic legs and snap crotch closing.  Purchased trim.  Pattern is uncut, factory folded, complete with directions. The envelope has shelf wear.  Dated 1993.


Size:  14-16-18
Bust:  36-38-40&quot;
Waist: 28-30-32&quot;
Hips:  38-40-42&quot;
